            "subtype": "ability",
            "success": "The creature is stupefied 1 for 1 round and is then temporarily immune to Captivating Lure for 24 hours.",
            "text": "The kelpie instills an overwhelming attraction to itself within the mind of a single creature within 60 feet. The target perceives the kelpie as a desirable person (if the kelpie is in humanoid form) or a magnificent steed (if the kelpie is in equine form) and must attempt a DC 23 Will saving throw.",
